data.description: Spacious home in Greenleaf!  Open floor plan with split bedrooms. Lots of space with oversized Master bedroom and a terrific walk-in closet! New HVAC in 2020. New front porch deck in 2021. Trey ceilings. Oak cabinets. Laundry room directly off the kitchen.  New hardwood floors installed in living room, dining area, and adjacent hallway. Ceiling fans in every bedroom. Escape into a wooded oasis with its own garden shed, concrete patio and fenced yard. Light fixture in dining and kitchen do not remain.
